         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Expectation is to compare and match customer's actual purchase order data against the created sales order (SO). Purchase order data either from the actual EDI messages if electronically sent or via attached PO documents.&#10; if manually created then compare it against the created sales order or via SAP standard tables (header details VBAK and line item details VBAP)."/>
